[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0229","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0229.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0098","title":"Sendmail SMTP HELO 命令缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Sendmail SMTP 服务在处理 HELO 命令时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者无需认证即可向目标服务器的 25 端口发送特制的 HELO 请求触发该漏洞，成功利用可导致任意代码执行或服务崩溃，攻击者借此可完全控制服务器或隐藏恶意活动痕迹。该漏洞影响多个版本的 Sendmail，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0098"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-04-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:34.903","remediation":"立即升级 Sendmail 至 8.9.0 或更高版本（该版本修复了 SMTP HELO 命令缓冲区溢出问题）。SLMail 用户应升级至 3.0 及以上版本，Mercury Mail Server 用户升级至最新版本。如无法立即升级，可在防火墙层面限制 SMTP（TCP 25）端口仅允许可信来源访问，同时在 Sendmail 配置中限制 HELO 命令输入长度作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0098"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0229.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0442","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0442.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0257","title":"Linux Kernel IP Fragmentation Nestea 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"CVE-1999-0257 即 Nestea 变种 Teardrop IP 碎片拒绝服务攻击，攻击者向目标系统发送精心构造的、偏移量重叠的畸形 IP 分片数据包，目标系统在重组这些分片时因算法缺陷导致内存计算错误，引发系统崩溃或重启。该漏洞无需认证即可远程利用，影响 Linux Kernel 2.6.20.1 及众多早期操作系统版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0257"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-04-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:00.990","remediation":"升级 Linux 内核至 2.6.20.1 以上版本（如 2.6.21+），该漏洞已在后续版本中修复。无法升级时，可在 iptables 中添加规则丢弃畸形 IP 分片包：iptables -A INPUT -f -m limit --limit 100/s --limit-burst 100 -j ACCEPT 或使用防火墙过滤分片重叠的恶意数据包作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0257","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5917e2b15694e167c1fd9ad85775b2bdfc5fe29c/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0257.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0257","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0257.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0257.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0257.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-5h5w-wrfr-qmhc/GHSA-5h5w-wrfr-qmhc.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/N/nestea.nasl","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0257.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0442.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0761","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0761.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0507","title":"开源路由器弱口令漏洞","description":"路由器、防火墙或其他网络设备上存在具有弱口令（可猜测密码）的账户，攻击者无需身份认证即可通过远程网络尝试常见或默认凭据登录设备。该漏洞影响各类使用弱密码或默认账户配置的网络设备，攻击条件为攻击者能够与目标设备建立网络连通并访问其管理或服务端口。利用方式为通过暴力破解或字典攻击猜测账户密码，成功登录后可获取设备控制权，进而篡改路由策略、绕过防火墙规则或作为内网跳板，造成严重的安全风险。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0507"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-04-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:32.553","remediation":"立即更换所有网络设备（路由器、防火墙等）上的默认/弱口令为强密码（至少12位，含大小写字母、数字和特殊字符），禁用默认管理账户（如admin/root），启用账户锁定策略（连续5次失败后锁定30分钟），并定期（每90天）更换口令。对于支持TACACS+/RADIUS的设备，建议启用集中认证。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0507","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/6e5939e8074723d33adaf5b2f8b0352edab9ba8d/1999/CVE-1999-0507.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c271719fd48dcc28619dc324e441b822d7b4bace/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0507.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0507","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/1e2d061a60b9c6823d20cc72e51f709fadad54d2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0507.json","https://github.com/DefectDojo/django-DefectDojo/blob/d9905eb7656178d3e59e0bf8f1d53a9ee9e50186/unittests/scans/openvas/many_vuln.xml","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0507.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0507.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x84000/83210/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/jbeasl7/openvas-feed-sync-local/blob/7c8dc35196ef4eb644a4c5a923e3428412a226aa/openvas-feeds/nvt-feed/pre2008/DDI_WhatsUp_Default.nasl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0761.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0761.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0804","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0804.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0537","title":"Internet Explorer 及 Netscape Navigator 活动内容执行漏洞","description":"该漏洞源于网页浏览器（如 Internet Explorer 或 Netscape Navigator）的安全配置缺陷，允许网页中嵌入的 ActiveX、Java、JavaScript 等活跃内容在客户端自动执行。远程攻击者可利用此配置缺陷构造恶意网页，诱导用户访问后即可在用户浏览器上下文中执行任意脚本代码或 ActiveX 控件，导致敏感信息泄露、会话劫持或系统权限被滥用。该漏洞影响 Internet Explorer 及 Netscape Navigator 等主流浏览器，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0537"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-04-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:36.140","remediation":"建议升级至现代浏览器（如 Chrome/Firefox/Edge），这些浏览器默认启用沙盒隔离与内容安全策略。如必须使用 IE，将 Internet 安全区域中「ActiveX 控件和插件」「Java 小程序」「脚本」均设为「禁用」，并通过组策略强制推送；同时在 Web 服务器层配置 Content-Security-Policy 标头限制脚本来源。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0537"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0804.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0815","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0815.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0551","title":"HP OpenMail 任意命令执行漏洞","description":"HP OpenMail 邮件系统存在安全配置缺陷，由于对打印请求的访问控制权限设置不当，拥有本地访问权限的攻击者可通过发送恶意构造的打印请求绕过安全限制，在目标系统上以 OpenMail 服务进程权限执行任意系统命令。该漏洞影响 HP OpenMail 服务器，攻击者需具备本地用户权限，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0551"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-04-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:37.113","remediation":"限制 HP OpenMail 打印服务仅允许受信任用户提交打印请求，在 OpenMail 配置中禁用不必要的命令执行接口，并升级到厂商修复此问题的最新版本。同时在系统层面限制 OpenMail 运行账户的最小权限，防止恶意打印请求执行任意命令。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9804-078"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0815.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0152","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0152.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0060","title":"Lucent Ascend 系列路由器 Discard Service 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Lucent Ascend MAX 5.0/Pipeline 6.0/TNT 1.0/2.0 路由器存在拒绝服务漏洞。攻击者无需身份认证，只需向目标路由器的 discard 端口（UDP 端口 9，被 Java Configurator 工具使用）发送特制的畸形数据包，即可触发该漏洞，导致路由器服务崩溃或无法正常响应，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Lucent Ascend MAX、Pipeline 及 TNT 系列路由器，需引起相关运维人员重视。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0060"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1998-03-16T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:29.030","remediation":"在受影响路由器上配置访问控制列表（ACL），禁止外部来源向 UDP 端口 9（Discard 端口）发送数据包；如无需 Java Configurator 功能，建议在系统配置中禁用 Discard 服务。鉴于 Ascend MAX/Pipeline/TNT 系列已停止技术支持且无官方补丁可用，建议迁移至受支持的现代路由器硬件以彻底消除风险。作为临时缓解措施，可在网络边界防火墙处过滤目标端口为 UDP 9 的入站流量。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ascend.com/2695.html","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19555","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0060.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0060","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0060.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0060.md","https://github.com/eldondev/Snort/blob/34bdcf6a7a638b55c7c04f77ef1efa526ad08e33/doc/signatures/281.txt","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0060.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-5j44-w6q9-hxx4/GHSA-5j44-w6q9-hxx4.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/dos.rules","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/A/ascend_kill.nasl","https://github.com/magicsword-io/Magic-SigExplorer/blob/2c28b91b003429a144a687199ee99ebd26f1a343/Magic-SigExplorer/docs/cve_report.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0152.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0451","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0451.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0266","title":"Info2www CGI 输入处理远程命令执行漏洞","description":"Info2www 是一个用于将 GNU Info 文档转换为 HTML 格式的 CGI 脚本程序。该脚本对用户输入的参数缺乏充分的过滤与验证，远程攻击者可通过向 info2www CGI 脚本发送特制请求，利用输入处理缺陷实现任意文件读取或远程命令执行。该漏洞影响 Info2www 1.0 及 1.1 版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高危。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0266"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1998-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:02.100","remediation":"立即从 Web 服务器移除 info2www CGI 脚本目录（通常位于 /cgi-bin/info2www），或删除 info2www 文件。如仍需此类功能，改用维护中的替代方案（如 Pinfo）。通过 Web 服务器配置限制 CGI 目录执行权限，确保仅授权用户可执行，并在 WAF 层过滤包含特殊字符（如 |、;、`、$()）的 CGI 请求参数。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1995","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20430","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/1999/CVE-1999-0266.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0cda26301f5b3e56ace35e3d98835812d878db41/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0266.json","https://github.com/geeknik/the-nuclei-templates/blob/36a6d14bce3293907a83afb498caec5fd45b1777/CVE-1999-0266.yaml","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0266","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/36c16d53eb6071e39cfc3cf88e99f1b340ec913b/data/year/1999.txt","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-1999-0266.yaml","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0266.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0266.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-5j6c-65fm-f6cr/GHSA-5j6c-65fm-f6cr.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/web-cgi.rules"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0451.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0532","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0532.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0320","title":"Sun SunOS rpc.cmsd 任意文件覆盖提权漏洞","description":"SunOS/Solaris 系统的 rpc.cmsd（日历管理服务守护进程）存在任意文件覆写漏洞。rpc.cmsd 以 root 权限运行，由于对用户提交的 RPC 参数缺乏充分的路径验证，未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过向目标系统的日历管理服务发送特制 RPC 请求，覆写任意系统文件，从而获取 root 访问权限。该漏洞影响 SunOS 5.3 至 5.5.1（Solaris 2.3 至 2.5.1）版本，CVSS 评分 9.3，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":9.3,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0320"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:08.750","remediation":"针对 SunOS/Solaris 2.x 系统，安装 Sun Security Bulletin #166 提供的对应版本补丁：Solaris 2.3 安装 101318 补丁、Solaris 2.4 安装 101945 补丁、Solaris 2.5 安装 103093 补丁、Solaris 2.5.1 安装 103094 补丁。如业务不需要日历管理服务，可停止 rpc.cmsd 守护进程（/etc/init.d/calendar stop）并注释 rpc 绑定条目作为临时缓解。对于仍在运行的遗留系统，建议迁移至 Oracle Solaris 11 及以上受支持版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/166"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0532.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0545","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0545.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0330","title":"Linux bdash 游戏缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Linux bdash 游戏程序存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可通过向游戏程序提交特制的输入数据触发缓冲区溢出，成功利用后可获取 root 权限，实现本地权限提升。该漏洞影响运行 bdash 游戏的 Linux 系统，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。攻击前提是攻击者拥有系统的本地账户访问权限。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0330"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:10.070","remediation":"立即移除 bdash 游戏的 setuid root 权限位（执行 chmod u-s /usr/games/bdash），或直接卸载 bsdgames 软件包以彻底消除提权风险。如确需保留该游戏，应升级至已修复缓冲区边界检查的修补版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602558319119&w=2"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0545.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0752","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0752.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0502","title":"Unix SSH 默认空口令远程登录漏洞","description":"Unix 系统存在默认账户或空密码配置漏洞，当管理员未设置密码或密码为空时，攻击者可通过 SSH 服务使用常见默认用户名（如 root、admin）进行远程登录尝试。成功登录后可获系统完全控制权限，执行任意命令。该漏洞影响大量未正确配置账户安全的 Unix/Linux 系统，利用难度低、危害严重。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0502"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:31.960","remediation":"立即检查所有本地 Unix 系统账户，为每个账户设置强密码（至少 12 位，含大小写字母、数字及特殊字符）；删除或禁用无密码账户及默认测试账户；配置 `/etc/shadow` 确保密码哈希字段非空；启用 PAM 模块 `pam_pwquality.so` 强制密码复杂度策略，并在 SSH 配置中设置 `PermitEmptyPasswords no` 禁止空密码登录。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0502","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/41694","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/6e5939e8074723d33adaf5b2f8b0352edab9ba8d/1999/CVE-1999-0502.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/122439703ba8729c2a612b649ea87112305b8e28/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0502.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0502","https://github.com/ARPSyndicate/suricata-vedas/blob/fe24794ad36564b5bbc7c69101525011387b8650/1999/CVE-1999-0502.rules","https://github.com/e-m-b-a/emba/blob/968abdc74763b43a3cdd216fbb1950cab484f982/config/msf_cve-db.txt","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/bc69cd1e5221f68ef56bd10c5c61adf76a19f0fc/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0502.json","https://github.com/vulncheck-oss/0day.today.archive/blob/3664abdd71985a44aff3260896a8f36e2f4a9682/remote-exploits/20781.txt","https://github.com/gottburgm/Exploits/blob/fd340a05cbec416e89bfae898e27bf5fcb429101/MSFExploits/DELL/MSF/Idrac_infos.txt","https://github.com/DefectDojo/django-DefectDojo/blob/d9905eb7656178d3e59e0bf8f1d53a9ee9e50186/unittests/scans/openvas/many_vuln.xml","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/account_lp.nasl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0752.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1150","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1150.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0795","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"inputTokens\":16297,\"outputTokens\":35,\"totalTokens\":16332}}","description":"标签之间。<value>Unix 系统的 NIS+（网络信息服务增强版）rpc.nisd 服务器存在安全漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可执行特定的 RPC 调用，借此获取目标系统的敏感信息、禁用安全日志记录或篡改 NIS+ 缓存数据。该漏洞影响运行 NIS+ 服务的 Unix/Linux 系统，攻击者可通过网络直接利用该缺陷，导致系统信息泄露或服务可用性受损。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0795"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:04.423","remediation":"建议立即安装 Sun 针对 NIS+ 的安全补丁（如 Solaris 2.6/7/8 对应补丁 ID 107181-xx 或 107182-xx），升级至最新受支持版本。如无法打补丁，可在 /etc/hosts.allow 和 /etc/hosts.deny 中限制 rpc.nisd 的访问来源，仅允许可信网段连接，并在防火墙上阻断对 RPC 端口映射服务（111/TCP,UDP）和 NIS+ 服务端口（通常为 32771/TCP,UDP）的未授权访问。若业务允许，建议停用 NIS+ 并迁移至 LDAP 目录服务。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0795","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c271719fd48dcc28619dc324e441b822d7b4bace/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0795.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0795","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0795.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/1e2d061a60b9c6823d20cc72e51f709fadad54d2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0795.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/990f1c1359f92984694d3e78664624bc14ed923f/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-g8p5-fw36-3r3c/GHSA-g8p5-fw36-3r3c.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0795.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000267.txt","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idinfor","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_infor.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1150.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0484","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0484.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0290","title":"Qbik WinGate Telnet Proxy 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Qbik WinGate Telnet 代理服务存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者通过向目标系统的 Telnet 代理端口发起大量本地主机连接请求，可耗尽代理服务资源导致服务崩溃，无法正常处理后续合法连接。该漏洞影响 Qbik WinGate 的 Telnet 代理模块，攻击者无需身份认证即可远程触发，风险等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0290"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-02-21T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:04.970","remediation":"建议升级 WinGate 至 4.0 及以上版本，该漏洞已在后续迭代中修复。如无法升级，可在 WinGate 网关属性中禁用 telnet 代理服务（取消 Telnet Proxy 复选框），或在防火墙上限制对 telnet 代理端口（默认 23）的入站连接数量，仅允许可信 IP 访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0290","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0290.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0290","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0290.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0290.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0290.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-m634-4fwc-9xqc/GHSA-m634-4fwc-9xqc.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/W/wingate_denial.nasl","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0290.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0484.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0537","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0537.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0323","title":"FreeBSD mmap 函数访问控制绕过漏洞","description":"FreeBSD 操作系统内核中的 mmap 内存映射函数存在文件属性绕过漏洞，本地攻击者可通过调用 mmap 系统接口，绕过文件系统的保护机制，修改被设置为仅追加（append-only）或不可变（immutable）属性的文件内容。攻击者需要具备目标系统的本地账户权限，通过编写恶意程序调用 mmap 对受保护文件进行写入操作，可导致篡改系统关键配置文件、日志文件或安全策略，破坏系统完整性。该漏洞影响多个 FreeBSD 版本，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0323"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-02-20T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:09.107","remediation":"建议升级至 NetBSD 1.4+ 或 FreeBSD 3.0+ 版本，其中已修复 mmap(2) 系统调用对不可变/仅追加文件的权限检查缺陷。对于 NetBSD 1.3/1.3.1，可应用的补丁（来自 ftp://ftp.NetBSD.ORG/pub/NetBSD/misc/security/patches/19980509-mmap）。如无法升级临时缓解措施，可将系统 securelevel 提升至 1 以上并避免在多进程间对设定了 append-only/immutable 标志的文件使用共享可写 mmap。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b8581edcbd9fb1606112c43470d0a7cb92a751f8/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0323.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0323","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0323.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f6ced4f7862026f4207c9708deb4edf129c83fc5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0323.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/057c97aa60eb958a2d272c7164e35c156db63b6c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-r5jc-68gw-7fmq/GHSA-r5jc-68gw-7fmq.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x83000/82264/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0323.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--c2ea8a31-4149-4cb6-8c91-11842551ba1b.json","https://github.com/Ethishh/securin_assessment/blob/e6ce9197b6593ae46f3f5646d268181eea6cbb31/cve_sync.log","https://github.com/zephyros1603/RadiantProcessors/blob/7d44cb1cd4b9e088fbe463f1b19be50a04c2efe8/Backend/RAG/data/allitems.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0537.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0411","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0411.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0225","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 SMB 登录请求长度错误拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Windows NT 4.0 的 SMB 登录验证服务在处理畸形登录请求时存在逻辑缺陷，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过发送实际数据大小与指定大小不符的特制 SMB 登录请求包，导致目标系统 LSASS 进程崩溃或系统蓝屏，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 所有版本，攻击条件简单，无需用户交互。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0225"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-02-14T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:57.050","remediation":"安装 Windows NT 4.0 Service Pack 6a (SP6a) 以修复 SMB 登录请求中数据大小校验缺失导致的拒绝服务漏洞。同时建议在网络防火墙层面阻断来自不可信网络的 SMB 端口（TCP 139/445）入站流量。由于 Windows NT 4.0 已终止支持超过 20 年，长期缓解措施应迁移至受支持的 Windows Server 版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.microsoft.com/technet/support/kb.asp?ID=180963","http://www.nai.com/nai_labs/asp_set/advisory/25_windows_nt_dos_adv.asp","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0225.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b78238ce198ba9bb84cf32286dd81a9973f793b6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0225.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0225","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/36c16d53eb6071e39cfc3cf88e99f1b340ec913b/data/year/1999.txt","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/b253eed42806cfea7592c1858184a214ab406ebe/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0225.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0225.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0225.md","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0225.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000260.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/d6641cf4b3c3f049679d3cd7a1e7c74ad9ced77c/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0411.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0443","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0443.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0258","title":"Microsoft Windows 95/NT 4.0 IP Fragmentation 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows 95 和 Windows NT 4.0 的 IP 碎片重组模块存在缺陷，远程攻击者可通过发送特制的畸形 IP 分片数据包（Bonk 变种），利用 UDP 协议的分片偏移量计算错误，导致目标系统内核崩溃或蓝屏死机，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞无需认证即可远程触发，影响 Windows 95 及 Windows NT 4.0 所有版本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0258"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-02-13T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:01.117","remediation":"升级至 Windows 2000 或更高版本系统，已不受此漏洞影响。若因特殊原因仍运行 Windows 95/NT 4.0，安装 Microsoft 1999 年安全更新 MS99-017（KB191725）可修复 IP 分段重组校验逻辑。临时缓解措施：在路由器/防火墙上阻断进入内网的畸形 IP 分片包，或限制入站 ICMP 流量降低攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=88901842000424&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5917e2b15694e167c1fd9ad85775b2bdfc5fe29c/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0258.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0258","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0258.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0258.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0258.json","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/B/bonk.nasl","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0258.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154000_154100.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/e7bd3e92452a8dc8da42d94ae3ba208936d5a5b9/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0443.toml"}]